comment_body: Didn't see that one coming. Nice job!
Niiiiiiiiiice!!! Wish I could upvote it more than a couple of times. What was your inspiration for it?

Alabama is not so sweet anymore.. :x Memes aside, this was nice! I thought the twist was going to be something like “Girl is like, 13 and does not realize that she is being groomed by a bad guy.” 

The mysterious magician guy was pretty cool!
